# Richer Expect matchers -- NotText (the frame must NOT contain substr),
# Line N (line N, 0-indexed, trimmed of trailing space, equals text
# exactly), and Width N (the frame's widest line, in display cells, equals
# N exactly). Source is the same sample.ctml the core DSL example
# (sample_test.ctml) renders.

Source sample.ctml
Set Width 40

Data session.title "Welcome"
Data version "1.0"
Rows items 3

Expect NotText "Goodbye"
Expect Line 0 "Welcome"
Expect Width 40
